{"tid":1023751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔識死】強國遊客「玩命」暴力搖晃 鐵索橋斷裂6人懸空","createTime":"2019-02-16T04:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T09:36:32.000Z","uid":23635,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ac79ce12a82f50d8399b19c7ecc8db4f2f69a028","tid":1023751,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190216/59262839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190216%2F59262839&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=dfc2670f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190216%2F59262839&h=1df4f6f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190216/59262839</a><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年期間，內地遊客湧到各地景區度歲。廣東省陽江市上周發生嚇人意外，當地一個景區的鐵索橋，有遊客在橋上猛烈搖晃，令到鐵索橋斷裂，多名遊客被半天吊。事後當局要求景區取消這個項目。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體昨日報道這宗發生在年初四（8日）下午的事故，涉事的是位於陽東區新洲鎮北桂村北桂園山莊的鐵索橋，這條橋跨越一條10米闊、水深1米左右的小河，鐵索橋離河面約2.5米。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者指出，當日下午3時許，6名遊客走過鐵索橋，一名遊客突然在橋上不斷地用力搖晃、左右猛搖兩邊的扶手，在鐵索橋上製造「波浪」，幾名遊客又加入「搖擺」。約兩分鐘後其中一邊的扶手鋼索斷裂，幾名年輕遊客因此身體失衡，腳一踩空，就被安全繩懸吊在半空。"},{"pid":"d041d78c8132ee97d54ade74aab298b142761fa4","tid":1023751,"uid":134908,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:45:30.000Z","msg":"可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e7e0f86c862e040fa1929f0e53de867495f3e4","tid":1023751,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"鬼國之日常"},{"pid":"31e77c96ca9194136430b7f497403cb8a9da50d5","tid":1023751,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"屌 本身以為好高<br />\n原來跌落去最多浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d89e01c8284f53daae9cf0f6764e648b81a963","tid":1023751,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score